Package: deepIdeology
Type: Package
Title: Scale Ideological Slant of Twitter Posts
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Gottlieb
Maintainer: Alex Gottlieb <Alexander.R.Gottlieb.GR@dartmouth.edu>
Description: This package allows users to identify the ideological leanings of Twitter posts with benchmark accuracy
    using a Long Short-Term Memory recurrent neural network model trained on a data set of Tweets labeled through
    the Amazon Mechanical Turk crowd-sourcing platform. The best-performing models are able to classify Tweets are 
    liberal- or conservative-leaning with 86.90% accuracy and are able to capture both directionality and degree of
    slant.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.4),
    dplyr,
    keras (<= 2.2.0)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1.9000
Imports: 
    purrr
